snippet.title: IRON MARINES Teaser (Official)
snippet.description:
A colony under attack! Hostile alien lifeforms attacking in overwhelming numbers! A small force of soldiers steps forward!
Do you want to know more? Subscribe at http://www.ironhidegames.com/

Get ready for a whole new battle in a whole new universe!
Get ready for exclamation marks in every sentence!
Get ready for IRON MARINES!
Coming soon to a Solar System near you.
